translation: 此函数仅供内部测试。不要在生产代码中使用

english: Returns a copy of this Object and all its children. The copy's Parent is nil
translation: 返回此对象及其所有子级的副本。副本的父项为零

english: Returns a boolean if this Instance is of type 'className' or a is a subclass of type 'className'. If 'className' is not a valid class type in ROBLOX, this function will always return false. More info
translation: 返回一个布尔值，判断此 Instance 是否为 'className' 类型或 'className' 类型的子类。若 'className' 不是 ROBLOX 中的有效类类型，此函数将始终返回 false。更多信息

english: Returns the first child of this Instance that matches the first argument 'name'.  The second argument 'recursive' is an optional boolean (defaults to false) that will force the call to traverse down thru all of this Instance's descendants until it finds an object with a name that matches the 'name' argument.  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
translation: 返回与第一个参数 'name' 匹配的该实例的第一个子级。 第二个参数 'recursive' 是一个可选的布尔值 (默认为 false)，将强制调用遍历该实例的所有后代，直至找到名称与 'name' 参数匹配的对象为止。如果没有找到实例，该函数将返回零。

english: Returns the first child of this Instance that with a ClassName equal to 'className'.  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
translation: 返回此 Instance 中 ClassName 等于 'className' 的第一个子类。若未找到 Instance，此函数将返回空值。

english: Returns the first child of this Instance that :IsA(className).  The second argument 'recursive' is an optional boolean (defaults to false) that will force the call to traverse down thru all of this Instance's descendants until it finds an object with a name that matches the 'className' argument.  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
translation: 返回此 Instance 中符合 IsA(className) 的第一个子类。第二个参数 'recursive' 是一个可选布尔值 (默认为 false)，参数为 true 时将强制此调用遍历此 Instance 的所有后代直到其找到一个名称与 'className' 参数匹配的对象。若未找到 Instance，此函数将返回空值。

english: Returns the first ancestor of this Instance that matches the first argument 'name'.  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
translation: 返回此 Instance 的匹配第一个参数 'name' 的第一个祖先。若未找到 Instance，此函数将返回空值。

english: Returns the first ancestor of this Instance with a ClassName equal to 'className'.  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
translation: 返回此 Instance 的 ClassName 等于 'className' 的第一个祖先。若未找到 Instance，此函数将返回空值。

english: Returns the first ancestor of this Instance that :IsA(className).  The function will return nil if no Instance is found.
translation: 返回此 Instance 的符合 IsA(className) 的第一个祖先。若未找到 Instance，此函数将返回空值。

english: Returns a string that shows the path from the root node (DataModel) to this Instance.  This string does not include the root node (DataModel).
translation: 返回一个显示从根节点 (DataModel) 至此 Instance 的路径的字符串。此字符串不包括根节点 (DataModel)。

english: Returns a read-only table of this Object's children
translation: 返回此对象的子级的只读表

english: Returns an array containing all of the descendants of the instance. Returns in preorder traversal, or in other words, where the parents come before their children, depth first.
translation: 返回一个包含此实例的所有后代的数组。返回值为前序遍历，换言之，父类将排在子类的前面，深度优先。

english: Deprecated. Use ClearAllChildren() to get rid of all child objects, or Destroy() to invalidate this object and its descendants
translation: 已弃用。使用 ClearAllChildren() 去除所有子对象，或使用 Destroy() 使该对象及其后代失效

english: Removes all children (but not this object) from the workspace.
translation: 从工作区移除所有子类 (不包括此对象)。

english: Removes object and all of its children from the workspace. Disconnects object and all children from open connections. Object and children may not be usable after calling Destroy.
translation: 从工作区移除此对象及其所有子类。从开放连接断开此对象及其所有子类。在调用 Destroy 后此对象及其子类可能无法使用。

english: Fired when any of this object's ancestors change.  First argument 'child' is the object whose parent changed.  Second argument 'parent' is the first argument's new parent.
translation: 当此对象的任意祖先发生变动时触发。第一个参数 'child' 是父类发生变动的对象。第二个参数 'parent' 是第一个参数的新父类。

english: Fired after an Instance is parented to this object, or any of this object's descendants.  The 'descendant' argument is the Instance that is being added.
translation: 当一个 Instance 成为此对象或此对象的任意后代的父类时触发。 'descendant' 参数是被添加的 Instance。

english: Fired after an Instance is unparented from this object, or any of this object's descendants.  The 'descendant' argument is the Instance that is being added.
translation: 当一个 Instance 与此对象或此对象的任意后代脱离父类关系后触发。 'descendant' 参数是被添加的 Instance。

english: Fired after a property changes value.  The property argument is the name of the property
translation: 当一个属性的值发生变动时触发。属性参数是该属性的名称

english: Attempts to maintain a fixed orientation of its parent Part
translation: 尝试维持其父 Part 的固定朝向

english: The maximum torque that will be exerted on the Part
translation: 施加在部件上的最大扭矩

english: The dampening factor applied to this force
translation: 应用于此力的阻尼系数

english: The power continually applied to this force
translation: 应持续用于此力的功率

english: The cframe that this force is trying to orient its parent Part to.  Note: this force only uses the rotation of the cframe, not the position.
translation: 该力试图将其父部件定向到的 cframe。 注意: 此力仅使用 cframe 的旋转，而不是位置。

english: The maximum force that will be exerted on the Part
translation: 施加在部件上的最大力

english: The dampening factor applied to this force
translation: 应用于此力的阻尼系数

english: The power factor continually applied to this force
translation: 持续应用于此力的功率因数

english: The Vector3 that this force is trying to position its parent Part to.
translation: 此力试图将其父部件定位到的 Vector3。

english: A propulsion system that mimics a rocket
translation: 一种模仿火箭的推进系统

english: The maximum force that will be exerted on the Part in each axis
translation: 在每个轴上施加在部件上的最大力

english: The amount of power we add to the system.  The higher the power, the quicker the force will achieve its goal.
translation: 我们添加到系统的功率数值。功率越高，力达成目标的速度就越快。

english: The velocity this system tries to achieve.  How quickly the system reaches this velocity (if ever) is defined by P.
translation: 该系统试图达到的速度。P 定义系统达到此速度的速度 (如果有的话)。

english: When parented to a physical part, BodyForce will continually exert a force upon its parent object.
translation: 当成为物理部件的子类时，BodyForce 将对其父对象持续施加一个力。

english: The power continually applied to this force
translation: 不断在此力上施加的力量

english: The Vector3 location of where to apply the force to.
translation: 将力施加到的 Vector3 位置。

english: This Service-level object is the container for all Team objects in a level. A map that supports team games must have a Teams service. More info
translation: 此 Service 级对象是一个关卡中所有 Team 对象的容器。支持组队游戏的地图必须拥有 Team 服务。更多信息

english: Returns a read-only table of players which are on this team.
translation: 返回一个包含在此队伍中的所有玩家的只读表。

english: The Team class is used to represent a faction in a team game. The only valid location for a Team object is under the Teams service. More info
translation: Team 类用于代表组队游戏中的一个阵营。Team 对象的唯一有效位置是在 Teams 服务下。更多信息

english: The name of the player who is currently editing the script in Team Create.
translation: 目前正在组队创作中编辑此脚本的玩家名称。

english: This property is under development. Do not use
translation: 此属性正在开发中。请不要使用

english: A script that runs on clients, NOT servers.  LocalScripts can only run when parented under one of the following:1) A player's Backpack.2) A player's Character model.3) A player's PlayerGui.4) A player's PlayerScripts.5) The ReplicatedFirst service.
translation: 在客户端而非服务器上运行的脚本。LocalScript 只有作为以下类的子类时才能运行: 1) 玩家的背包。2) 玩家的 Character 模型。3) 玩家的 PlayerGui。4) 玩家的 PlayerScripts。5) ReplicatedFirst 服务。

english: A construct used to group Parts and other objects together, also allows manipulation of multiple objects.
translation: 用于将 Part 和其他对象组合在一起的构造，允许对多个对象进行操作。

english: Breaks all surface joints contained within
translation: 断开包含在内的所有表面关节

english: Returns a CFrame that has position of the centroid of all Parts in the Model.  The rotation matrix is either the rotation matrix of the user-defined PrimaryPart, or if not specified then  a part in the Model chosen by the engine.
translation: 返回一个包含 Model 内所有 Part 的质心位置的 CFrame。旋转矩阵可以是用户指定的 PrimaryPart 的旋转矩阵，若用户未指定则由引擎选择 Model 中的一个部件。

english: Returns a Vector3 that is union of the extents of all Parts in the model.
translation: 返回 Model 中所有 Part 的范围并集 Vector3。

english: Creates the appropriate SurfaceJoints between all touching Parts contrained within the model. Technically, this function calls MakeJoints() on all Parts inside the model.
translation: 在模型中约束的所有接触部件之间创建适当的 SurfaceJoint。从技术上而言，此函数在模型内的所有部件上调用MakeJoints()。

english: Moves the centroid of the Model to the specified location, respecting all relative distances between parts in the model.
translation: 将 Model 的质心移至指定位置，保留模型中所有部件之间的相对距离。

english: Rotates all parts in the model to the orientation that was set using SetIdentityOrientation().  If this function has never been called, rotation is reset to GetModelCFrame()'s rotation.
translation: 将模型中的所有部件旋转至通过 SetIdentityOrientation() 设置的指定朝向。若此函数先前从未被调用，旋转值将重置为 GetModelCFrame() 的旋转值。

english: Takes the current rotation matrix of the model and stores it as the model's identity matrix. The rotation is applied when ResetOrientationToIdentity() is called.
translation: 取模型的当前旋转矩阵并将其储存为该模型的单位矩阵。调用 ResetOrientationToIdentity() 时应用旋转值。

english: Similar to MoveTo(), except instead of moving to an explicit location, we use the model's current CFrame location and offset it.
translation: 与 MoveTo() 类似，但不直接移动至明确位置，而是使用模型的当前 CFrame 位置进行偏移。

english: Returns the cframe of the Model.PrimaryPart. If PrimaryPart is nil, then this function will throw an error.
translation: 返回 Model.PrimaryPart 的 CFrame。若 PrimaryPart 为空值，此函数会报错。

english: Sets the cframe of the Model.PrimaryPart. If PrimaryPart is nil, then this function will throw an error. This also sets the cframe of all descendant Parts relative to the cframe change to PrimaryPart.
translation: 设置 Model.PrimaryPart 的 CFrame。若 PrimaryPart 为空值，此函数会报错。还会设置与 PrimaryPart 的 CFrame 改动相关的所有后代 Part 的 CFrame。

english: A Part that serves as a reference for the Model's CFrame. Used in conjunction with GetModelPrimaryPartCFrame and SetModelPrimaryPartCFrame. Use this to rotate/translate all Parts relative to the PrimaryPart.
translation: 作为 Model 的 CFrame 的参照物的 Part。与 GetModelPrimaryPartCFrame 和 SetModelPrimaryPartCFrame 结合使用。使用此方法旋转/转变与 PrimaryPart 相关的所有 Part。

english: The root of ROBLOX's parent-child hierarchy (commonly known as game after the global variable used to access it)
translation: ROBLOX 的父子层次结构的根 (对于用来访问它的全局变量，俗称“游戏”)

english: Returns true if the game has finished loading, false otherwise.  Check this before listening to the Loaded signal to ensure a script knows when a game finishes loading.
translation: 若游戏已加载完毕则返回 true，否则返回 false。在监听 Loaded 信号前先检查此项以确保脚本知道游戏何时完成加载。

english: Fires when the game finishes loading.  Use this to know when to remove your custom loading gui.  It is best to check IsLoaded() before connecting to this event, as the game may load before the event is connected to.
translation: 当游戏加载完毕时触发。使用此事件来获知何时应移除你的自定义加载界面。最好在连接至此事件前先检查 IsLoaded()，因为游戏可能在事件连接前载入。

english: Responsible for storing data across multiple user created places
translation: 负责在多个用户创建场景之间储存数据

english: Returns a data store with the given name and scope
translation: 返回具有指定名称和作用域的数据存储

english: Returns an ordered data store with the given name and scope
translation: 返回具有指定名称和作用域的经过排序的数据存储

english: Exposes functions for saving and loading data for the DataStoreService
translation: 公开用于为 DataStoreService 保存和加载数据的函数

english: Sets callback as a function to be executed any time the value associated with key is changed. It is important to disconnect the connection when the subscription to the key is no longer needed.
translation: 将回调设置为与键关联的值发生改动时执行的函数。不再需要订阅键时断开连接非常重要。

english: Returns the value of the entry in the DataStore with the given key
translation: 返回 DataStore 中指定键的条目的值

english: Increments the value of a particular key amd returns the incremented value
translation: 递增指定键的值并返回递增后的值

english: Sets the value of the key. This overwrites any existing data stored in the key
translation: 设置键的值。此操作会覆盖键中储存的现有数据

english: Retrieves the value of the key from the website, and updates it with a new value. The callback until the value fetched matches the value on the web. Returning nil means it will not save.
translation: 从网站检索键的值，并更新为新值。回调直到从网站获取的值与该值相匹配。返回空值表示无法保存。

english: A type of DataStore where values must be positive integers. This makes OrderedDataStore suitable for leaderboard related scripting where you are required to order large amounts of data efficiently.
translation: 一种 DataStore 类型，其值必须为正整数。这使得 OrderedDataStore 适用于需要给大量数据高效排序的排行榜相关脚本。

english: Returns a DataStorePages object. The length of each page is determined by pageSize, and the order is determined by isAscending. minValue and maxValue are optional parameters which will filter the result.
translation: 返回一个 DataStorePages 对象。每页的长度由 pageSize 决定，顺序由 isAscending 决定。minValue 和 maxValue 为用于过滤结果的可选参数。

english: Where the Camera's focus is.  Any rotation of the camera will be about this subject.
translation: 镜头的焦点所在位置。对镜头的一切旋转都将围绕此对象进行。

english: Defines how the camera will behave. More info
translation: 定义镜头的行为方式。更多信息

english: The current position and rotation of the Camera.  For most CameraTypes, the rotation is set such that the CoordinateFrame lookVector is pointing at the Focus.
translation: 镜头的当前位置和旋转值。对于大多数 CameraType 而言，旋转值为 CoordinateFrame 的 lookVector 指向 Focus。

english: The current position and rotation of the Camera.  For most CameraTypes, the rotation is set such that the CoordinateFrame lookVector is pointing at the Focus.
translation: 镜头的当前位置和旋转值。对于大多数 CameraType 而言，旋转值为 CoordinateFrame 的 lookVector 指向 Focus。

english: The current angle, or width, of what the camera can see.  Current acceptable values are from 20 degrees to 80.
translation: 镜头当前可见的角度或宽度。当前可接受的值为 20 至 80 度。

english: The current CoordinateFrame that the camera is looking at.  Note: it is not always guaranteed that the camera is always looking here.
translation: 镜头当前朝向的 CoordinateFrame 。注: 不能保证镜头总是看向这里。

english: Holds the x,y screen resolution of the viewport the camera is presenting (note: this can differ from the AbsoluteSize property of a full screen gui).
translation: 储存镜头所呈现的观察窗的屏幕分辨率 x,y 值 (注: 此数值可能与全屏图形界面的 AbsoluteSize 属性有所不同)。

english: The negative z-offset of the view frustum's near clipping plane.
translation: 视椎体近剪切平面的负 z 轴偏移

english: Returns the camera's current roll. Roll is defined in radians, and is stored as the delta from the camera's y axis default normal vector.
translation: 返回镜头的当前翻滚值。翻滚值以弧度为单位，并储存为镜头 y 轴默认法矢量的 delta 值。

english: Takes a 3D position in the world and projects it onto x,y coordinates of screen space. Returns two values, first is a Vector3 that has x,y position and z position which is distance from camera (negative if behind camera, positive if in front). Second return value is a boolean indicating if the first argument is an on-screen coordinate.
translation: 取世界中的一个 3D 位置并将其映射至屏幕空间的 x,y 坐标。返回两个值，第一个是包含 x,y 位置和定义与镜头距离的 z 位置 (负数为在镜头后，正数为在镜头前) 的 Vector3。第二个返回值是判断第一个参数是否为屏幕上的坐标的布尔值。

english: Takes a 2D screen position and produces a Ray object to be used for 3D raycasting. Input is x,y screen coordinates, and a (optional, defaults to 0) z position which sets how far in the camera look vector to start the ray origin.
translation: 取屏幕上的一个 2D 位置并生成一个用于 3D 光线投射的 Ray 对象。输入为 x,y 屏幕坐标，(可选，默认为0) 的 z 位置设置镜头看向光线原点的矢量距离。

english: Same as ScreenPointToRay, except no GUI offsets are taken into account. Useful for things like casting a ray from the middle of the Camera.ViewportSize
translation: 同 ScreenPointToRay，但不计入 GUI 偏移。适用于从 Camera.ViewportSize 中央投射光线等。

english: Same as WorldToScreenPoint, except no GUI offsets are taken into account.
translation: 同 WorldToScreenPoint，但不计入 GUI 偏移。

english: Sets the camera's current roll. Roll is defined in radians, and is stored as the delta from the camera's y axis default normal vector.
translation: 设置镜头的当前翻滚值。翻滚值以弧度为单位，并储存为镜头 y 轴默认法矢量的 delta 值。

english: Set to true, when a player joins a game, they get a character automatically, as well as when they die.  When set to false, characters do not auto load and will only load in using Player:LoadCharacter().
translation: 若设为真，玩家加入游戏和死亡时会自动获得一个角色。若设为假，角色不会自动加载，只有在使用 Player:LoadCharacter() 时才会加载。

english: A container whose contents are replicated to all clients and the server.
translation: 一个容器，其内容被复制到所有客户端和服务器。

english: A container whose contents are replicated to all clients (but not back to the server) first before anything else. Useful for creating loading guis, tutorials, etc.
translation: 一个容器，其内容在进行其他一切操作前先被复制到所有客户端 (但不会返回到服务器)。适用于创建载入图形界面、教程等。

english: Removes the default Roblox loading screen from view. Call this when you are ready to either show your own loading gui, or when the game is ready to play.
translation: 从视图中移除默认 Roblox 载入页面。当你准备好显示自己的载入界面或当游戏已准备就绪时调用。

english: A container whose contents are only on the server.
translation: 一个容器，其内容仅存在于服务器上。

english: A container whose contents should be scripts. Scripts that are added to the container are run on the server.
translation: 一个容器，其内容应为脚本。添加至该容器的脚本将在服务器上运行。

english: A service for interfacing with the current studio state from Lua.
translation: 用于与 Lua 的当前 Studio 状态进行交互的服务。

english: Responsible for all lighting aspects of the world (affects how things are rendered).
translation: 负责游戏世界中的所有照明外观 (影响物体的渲染方式)。

english: The number of minutes that the current time is past midnight.  If currently at midnight, returns 0.  Will return decimal values if not at an exact minute.
translation: 从午夜开始到当前时间的分钟数。若当前时间为午夜，则返回 0。若未处于准确分钟，将返回小数值。

english: Returns the lookVector (Vector3) of the moon. If this lookVector was used in a CFrame, the Part would face the moon.
translation: 返回月球的 lookVector (Vector3)。若此 lookVector 被用于 CFrame 中，Part 将面向月球。

english: Currently always returns 0.75. MoonPhase cannot be edited.
translation: 目前总是返回 0.75。MoonPhase 无法被编辑。

english: Returns the lookVector (Vector3) of the sun. If this lookVector was used in a CFrame, the Part would face the sun.
translation: 返回太阳的 lookVector (Vector3)。若此 lookVector 被用于 CFrame 中，Part 将面向太阳。

english: Sets the time to be a certain number of minutes after midnight.  This works with integer and decimal values.
translation: 设置时间为从午夜开始经过的一定分钟数。可为整数或小数值。

english: The hue of the global lighting.  Changing this changes the color tint of all objects in the Workspace.
translation: 全局照明的色调。修改此值会改变工作区中所有对象的颜色色调。

english: How much global light each Part in the Workspace receives. Standard range is 0 to 2 (0 being little light), but can be increased all the way to 10 (colors start to be appear very different at this value).
translation: 工作区中的每个 Part 能接收到多少全局光照。标准范围为 0 至 2 (0 为极少光照)，但也可以增加至 10 (从此数值开始色彩会显得极为不同)。

english: Exposure compensation amount. Applies a bias to the exposure level prior to the tonemap step. +1 indicates twice as much exposure and -1 means half as much exposure.
translation: 曝光补偿值。在色调映射步骤前对曝光级别应用偏差值。+1 代表曝光量加倍，-1 代表曝光量减半。

english: This property controls how blurry the shadows are.
translation: 此属性控制阴影的模糊程度。

english: The hue of global lighting on the bottom surfaces of an object.
translation: 物体底表面的全局照明色调。

english: The hue of global lighting on the top surfaces of an object.
translation: 物体顶表面的全局照明色调。

english: A Color3 value that changes the hue of the atmosphere, mixed with the sky color.
translation: 混合天空颜色改变气氛色调的 Color3 值。

english: The distance at which fog completely blocks your vision. This distance is relative to the camera position. Units are in studs
translation: 迷雾能完全阻隔你的视线的距离。此距离与镜头位置有关。单位为格

english: The distance at which the fog gradient begins. This distance is relative to the camera position. Units are in studs.
translation: 迷雾渐变开始的距离。此距离与镜头位置有关。单位为格。

english: The latitude position the level is placed at. This affects sun position. More info
translation: 关卡所在的纬度位置。此设定会影响太阳的位置。更多信息

english: Flag enabling shadows from sun and moon in the place
translation: 启用场景中太阳和月亮所造成的阴影的 flag

english: Effective ambient value for outdoors, effectively shadow color outdoors (requires GlobalShadows enabled)
translation: 户外有效环境值，户外有效阴影值 (需启用 GlobalShadows)

english: Flag enabling or disabling outlines on parts and terrain
translation: 启用或停用部件和地形的轮廓的 flag

english: Color the shadows appear as. Shadows are drawn mostly for characters, but depending on the lighting will also show for Parts in the Workspace.  Rendering settings can also affect if shadows are drawn.
translation: 阴影的显示颜色。大多数情况下只对角色绘制阴影，但根据照明条件，也可能显示工作区中 Part 的阴影。渲染设定也会影响是否绘制阴影。

english: A string that represent the current time of day. Time is in 24-hour clock format "XX::YY:ZZ", where X is hour, Y is minute, and Z is seconds.
translation: 代表一天中当前时间的字符串。时间使用 24 小时制时钟格式 "XX::YY:ZZ"，其中 X 代表小时，Y 代表分钟，Z 代表秒。

english: Fired whenever a property of Lighting is changed, or a skybox or atmosphere is added or removed. Skyboxes are of type 'Sky' these and 'Atmosphere' should be parented directly to lighting.
translation: 每当对 Lighting 属性进行更改及对天空盒或气氛进行添加或移除时即会触发。天空盒的类型为 'Sky'，其与 'Atmosphere' 应为 Lighting 的直接子项。

english: A service that provides utility in cleaning up objects
translation: 提供清理对象实用工具的服务

english: Adds an Instance into the debris service that will later be destroyed.  Second argument 'lifetime' is optional and specifies how long (in seconds) to wait before destroying the item. If no time is specified then the item added will automatically be destroyed in 10 seconds.
translation: 向稍后将被销毁的碎片服务添加一个 Instance。第二个参数 'lifetime' 为可选项，指定项目被销毁前的等待时间 (以秒为单位)。若不指定时间，则被添加的项目将在 10 秒后被自动销毁。

english: An enum that describes how a Player's camera is allowed to behave. More info.
translation: 描述 Player 的镜头的可用行为方式的枚举。更多信息。

english: Read-only. If true, this Player's persistent data can be loaded, false otherwise. Info on Data Persistence.
translation: 只读。若值为 true，此 Player 的持久性数据可被载入，值为 false 则相反。关于数据持久性的信息。

english: Loads in a new character for this player.  This will replace the player's current character, if they have one. This should be used in conjunction with Players.CharacterAutoLoads to control spawning of characters. This function only works from a server-side script (NOT a LocalScript).
translation: 为此玩家载入一个新角色。若该玩家已有角色，将取代其当前角色。应结合 Players.CharacterAutoLoads 使用，用于控制角色的再生。此函数仅适用于服务器端脚本 (非 LocalScript)。

english: Yields until the persistent data for this Player is ready to be loaded. Info on Data Persistence.
translation: 暂停直到此 Player 的持久性数据已准备好被载入。关于数据持久性的信息。"

english: Fired periodically after the user has been AFK for a while.  Currently this event is only fired for the *local* Player.  "time" is the time in seconds that the user has been idle.
translation: 用户进入 AFK (离开) 状态一段时间后定期触发。当前此事件仅针对 *本地* Player 触发。“time”是用户进入离开状态的时间 (以秒为单位)。

english: Returns parts in the area defined by the Region3, up to specified maxCount or 100, whichever is less
translation: 返回由 Region3 指定区域内的部件，最多 maxCount 或 100 个，以较小者为准

english: Returns parts in the area defined by the Region3, up to specified maxCount or 100, whichever is less
translation: 返回由 Region3 指定区域内的部件，最多 maxCount 或 100 个，以较小者为准

english: Return type is (BasePart, Vector3) if the ray hits.  If it misses it will return (nil, PointAtEndOfRay)
translation: 若光线命中，则返回类型 (BasePart, Vector3)。若未命中则返回R (nil, PointAtEndOfRay)

english: Return type is (BasePart, Vector3) if the ray hits.  If it misses it will return (nil, PointAtEndOfRay)
translation: 若光线命中，则返回类型 (BasePart, Vector3)。若未命中则返回R (nil, PointAtEndOfRay)

english: Boolean used to enable the new physics solver
translation: 布尔值，用于启用新物理解决器

english: Sets the height at which falling characters and parts are destroyed. This property is not scriptable and can only be set in Studio
translation: 设置下落的角色和部件会被破坏的高度。此属性不可用于脚本，只能在 Studio 中进行设置

english: Contains information regarding the Part's position and a matrix that defines the Part's rotation. Can read/write. More info
translation: 包含关于 Part 的位置的信息和定义 Part 旋转值的矩阵。可读写。更多信息

english: Determines whether physical interactions with other Parts are respected.  If true, will collide and react with physics to other Parts.  If false, other parts will pass thru instead of colliding
translation: 决定是否遵守与其他 Part 的物理学互动。若值为 true，将与其他 Part 碰撞和互动。若值为 false，其他部件会穿过而非碰撞

english: Determines whether or not physics acts upon the Part.  If true, part stays 'Anchored' in space, not moving regardless of any collision/forces acting upon it.  If false, physics works normally on the part.
translation: 决定 Part 是否遵守物理学原理。若值为真，部件会被“锚固”在空间中，不会因为对其造成的碰撞和力而移动。若值为 true，部件将遵守一般物理学原理。

english: If true the part will be massless when welded to another part that is not massless. The part will still have mass like a normal part if it is an assembly root part according to GetRootPart().
translation: 若值为 true，部件在接合至另一个非无质量的部件时将变为无质量。若部件是一个根据 GetRootPart() 确定的装配根部件，它仍会像一个正常部件一样具有质量。

english: An integer from -127 to 127. Compares before other all other part properties besides massless for deciding which part is the assembly root part according to GetRootPart().
translation: -127 到 127 之间的整数。在除无质量外的其他所有部件属性之前进行比较，以确定哪个部件是根据  GetRootPart() 确定的装配根部件。

english: A float value ranging from 0.0f to 1.0f. Sets how much the Part will rebound against another. a value of 1 is like a superball, and 0 is like a lead block.
translation: 0.0f 到 1.0f 之间的浮点值。设置 Part 相互间的反弹系数。值为 1 时相当于橡皮球，值为 0 时相当于铅块。

english: A float value ranging from 0.0f to 1.0f. Sets how much the Part will be able to slide. a value of 1 is no sliding, and 0 is no friction, so infinite sliding.
translation: 0.0f 到 1.0f 之间的浮点值。设置 Part 的滑行能力。值为 1 时无法滑动，值为 0 时无摩擦力，即可以无限滑行。

english: Determines whether building tools (in-game and studio) can manipulate this Part.  If true, no editing allowed.  If false, editing is allowed.
translation: 决定建造工具 (游戏内和 Studio 中) 是否可操作此 Part。值为 true 时不允许编辑。值为 false 时允许编辑。

english: Determines whether this Part casts a shadow.
translation: 决定此 Part 是否投射阴影。

english: Specifies the look and feel the Part should have. Note: this does not define the color the Part is, see BrickColor for that. More info
translation: 指定 Part 应有的外观和感觉。注: 不会定义 Part 的颜色，若需定义该值，请参阅 BrickColor。更多信息

english: Specifies how shiny the Part is. A value of 1 is completely reflective (chrome), while a value of 0 is no reflectance (concrete wall)
translation: 指定 Part 的光泽度。值为 1 时完全反射 (铬)，值为 0 时无反射 (混凝土墙)

english: Sets the value for the smallest change in size allowable by the Resize(NormalId, int) function.
translation: 设置 Resize(NormalId, int) 函数允许改变尺寸的最小改动值。

english: Sets the value for the faces allowed to be resized by the Resize(NormalId, int) function.
translation: 设置 Resize(NormalId, int) 函数允许改变尺寸的面的值。

english: Sets how visible an object is. A value of 1 makes the object invisible, while a value of 0 makes the object opaque.
translation: 设置物体的可见程度。值为 1 时物体不可见，值为 0 时物体完全不透明。

english: How fast the Part is traveling in studs/second. This property is NOT recommended to be modified directly, unless there is good reason.  Otherwise, try using a BodyForce to move a Part.
translation: Part 的行进速度，以格/秒为单位。除非理由充分，否则不推荐直接修改此属性。请尝试使用 BodyForce 来移动 Part。

english: Position relative to parent part, or global space if there is no parent.
translation: 相对父部件的位置，或无父部件时相对全局空间的位置。

english: Orientation relative to parent part, or global space if there is no parent.
translation: 相对父部件的朝向，或无父部件时相对全局空间的朝向。

english: Rotation around X, Y, and Z axis.  Rotations applied in YXZ order.
translation: 围绕 X、Y 和 Z 轴的旋转值。按 YXZ 顺序旋转。

english: Creates the appropriate SurfaceJoints with all parts that are touching this Instance (including internal joints in the Instance, as in a Model). This uses the SurfaceTypes defined on the surfaces of parts to create the appropriate welds. More info
translation: 使用接触到此 Instance 的所有 Part 创建适当的 SurfaceJoint (包括如 Model 等 Instance 中的内部关节)。利用部件表面定义的 SurfaceType 来创建适当的接合。更多信息

english: Destroys SurfaceJoints with all parts that are touching this Instance (including internal joints in the Instance, as in a Model).
translation: 销毁接触到此 Instance 的所有部件的 SurfaceJoint（包括 Instance 中的内部关节，如在 Model 中）。

english: Returns a number that is the mass of this Instance.  Mass of a Part is immutable, and is changed only by the size of the Part.
translation: 返回一个数字，该数字是此实例的质量。部件的质量是不变的，并且仅通过部件的大小进行更改。

english: Resizes a Part in the direction of the face defined by 'NormalId', by the amount specified by 'deltaAmount'. If the operation will expand the part to intersect another Instance, the part will not resize at all.  Return true if the call is successful, false otherwise.
translation: 根据 'NormalId' 定义的面的方向，根据 'deltaAmount' 指定的数值调整 Part 的大小。若此操作会拓展部件至其与其他 Instance 相交，则部件不会被调整大小。若调用成功返回 true，否则返回 false。

english: Fired when the part stops touching another part
translation: 当部件停止接触其他部件时触发

english: A plastic building block - the fundamental component of ROBLOX
translation: 一块塑料积木— ROBLOX 的基本组件

english: A container instance that syncs data between a single player and the server.  ScreenGui objects that are placed in this container will be shown to the Player parent only
translation: 一个容器实例，用于在单个玩家和服务器之间同步数据。放置在此容器中的 ScreenGui 对象只会对 Player 父类显示

english: Overrides the default selection adornment (used for gamepads). For best results, this should point to a GuiObject.
translation: 覆盖默认选择装饰 (用于游戏手柄)。为了获得最佳效果，应指向一个 GuiObject。

english: A container instance that contains LocalScripts.  LocalScript objects that are placed in this container will be exectue only when a Player is the parent.
translation: 一个包含 LocalScript 的容器实例。放置在此容器中的 LocalScript 对象只会在作为 Player 的子类时执行。

english: A container instance that contains LocalScripts.  LocalScript objects that are placed in this container will be copied to new Players on startup.
translation: 一个包含 LocalScript 的容器实例。放置在此容器中的 LocalScript 对象会在启动时复制给新玩家。

english: A container instance that contains LocalScripts.  LocalScript objects that are placed in this container will be copied to new characters on startup.
translation: 一个包含 LocalScript 的容器实例。放置在此容器中的 LocalScript 对象会在启动时复制给新角色。

english: The base class of ScreenGui, BillboardGui, and SurfaceGui.
translation: ScreenGui、BillboardGui 和 SurfaceGui 的基类。

english: The core GUI object on which tools are built.  Add Frames/Labels/Buttons to this object to have them rendered as a 2D overlay
translation: 打造工具所需的核心 GUI 对象。为对象添加帧/标签/按钮，将它们渲染为 2D 覆盖

english: A GUI that adorns an object in the 3D world.  Add Frames/Labels/Buttons to this object to have them rendered while attached to a 3D object
translation: 用于装饰 3D 世界中的对象的 GUI。为此对象添加 Frame/Label/Button，以便在附加到 3D 对象时进行渲染

english: The Object the billboard gui uses as its base to render from.  Currently, the only way to set this property is thru a script, and must exist in the workspace.  This will only render if the object assigned derives from BasePart.
translation: 排行榜 GUI 用作渲染的基础 Object。目前只能通过脚本设置此属性，且必须存在于工作区中。只有当指定对象派生自 BasePart 时才会进行渲染。

english: A read-only Vector2 value that is the GuiObject's current position (x,y) in pixel space, from the top left corner of the GuiObject.
translation: 一个表明 GuiObject 在像素空间中的当前位置 (x, y) 的只读 Vector2 值，以 GuiObject 的左上角为准。

english: A read-only Vector2 value that is the GuiObject's current size (width, height) in pixel space.
translation: 一个表明 GuiObject 在像素空间中的当前大小 (宽，高) 的只读 Vector2 值。

english: If true, this GuiObject can fire mouse events and will pass them to any GuiObjects layered underneath, while false will do neither.
translation: 若值为 true，此 GuiObject 可触发鼠标事件并将其传递给下层 GuiObject，若值为否则无上述功能。

english: If true, billboard gui does not get occluded by 3D objects, but always renders on the screen.
translation: 若值为 true，排行榜 GUI 不会被 3D 对象遮挡，而是始终渲染在屏幕上。

english: If true, billboard gui will render, otherwise rendering will be skipped.
translation: 若值为 true，排行榜 GUI 会被渲染，否则将会跳过渲染。

english: A Vector3 (x,y,z) defined in studs that will offset the gui from the extents of the 3d object it is rendering from.
translation: 一个定义 GUI 与其渲染的 3D 对象范围的相对偏移值的 Vector3 (x,y,z)，以格为单位。

english: Specifies a Player that the BillboardGui will not render to.
translation: 指定 BillboardGui 不会渲染的 Player。

english: A Vector3 (x,y,z) defined in studs that will offset the gui from the centroid of the 3d object it is rendering from
translation: 一个定义 GUI 与其渲染的 3D 对象质心的相对偏移值的 Vector3 (x,y,z)，以格为单位

english: A Vector2 (x,y) defined in studs that will offset the gui size from it's current size.
translation: 一个定义 GUI 与其当前大小的相对偏移值的 Vector2 (x,y)，以格为单位。

english: A UDim2 value describing the size of the BillboardGui. More information on UDim2 is available here. Relative values are defined as one-to-one with studs.
translation: 一个描述 BillboardGui 大小的 UDim2 值。更多关于 UDim2 的信息请参阅这里。所定义的相关值与格一一对应。

english: Specifies the amount of influence lighting has on the billboard gui. A value of 0 is unlit, 1 is fully lit. Fractional values blend from unlit to lit.
translation: 指定照明对排行榜 GUI 的影响力值。值为 0 时完全熄灭，值为 1 时完全点亮。中间的分数值表示从完全熄灭到完全点亮之间的状态。

english: Renders its contained GuiObjects flat against the face of a part.
translation: 渲染其包含的平放在一个部件的面上的 GuiObject。

english: The Object the surface gui uses as its base to render from.  Currently, the only way to set this property is thru a script, and must exist in the workspace.  This will only render if the object assigned derives from BasePart.
translation: 被此表面 GUI 用作渲染基础的 Object。目前只能通过脚本设置此属性，且必须存在于工作区。只有当指定对象派生自 BasePart 时才会进行渲染。

english: If true, this GuiObject can fire mouse events and will pass them to any GuiObjects layered underneath, while false will do neither.
translation: 若值为 true，此 GuiObject 可触发鼠标事件并将其传递给下层 GuiObject，若值为 false 则无上述功能。

english: If true, surface gui will render, otherwise rendering will be skipped.
translation: 若值为 true，表面 GUI 会被渲染，否则将会跳过渲染。

english: Specifies the amount of influence lighting has on the surface gui. A value of 0 is unlit, 1 is fully lit. Fractional values blend from unlit to lit.
translation: 指定照明对表面 GUI 的影响力值。值为 0 时完全熄灭，值为 1 时完全点亮。中间的分数值表示从完全熄灭到完全点亮之间的状态。

english: A read-only Vector2 value that is the GuiObject's current position (x,y) in pixel space, from the top left corner of the GuiObject.
translation: 一个表明 GuiObject 在像素空间中的当前位置 (x, y) 的只读 Vector2 值，以 GuiObject 的左上角为准。

english: A read-only Vector2 value that is the GuiObject's current size (width, height) in pixel space.
translation: 一个表明 GuiObject 在像素空间中的当前大小 (宽，高) 的只读 Vector2 值。

english: An object that describes a particular user input, such as mouse movement, touches, keyboard, and more.
translation: 一个描述特定用户输入的对象，如鼠标移动、触碰、键盘等。

english: An enum that describes what kind of input this object is describing (mousebutton, touch, etc.).  See Enum.UserInputType for more info.
translation: 一个描述此对象描述的输入类型 (鼠标按钮、触碰等) 的枚举。更多信息请参阅 Enum.UserInputType。

english: An enum that describes what state of a particular input (touch began, touch moved, touch ended, etc.). See Enum.UserInputState for more info.
translation: 一个描述特定输入的状态 (触碰开始、触碰移动、触碰结束等) 的枚举。更多信息请参阅 Enum.UserInputState。

english: A Vector3 value that describes a positional value of this input. For mouse and touch input, this is the screen position of the mouse/touch, described in the x and y components. For mouse wheel input, the z component describes whether the wheel was moved forward or backward.
translation: 一个描述此输入的位置值的 Vector3 值。针对鼠标和触碰输入，给出的是鼠标或触碰的屏幕位置，存放于 x 和 y 值中。针对鼠标滚轮输入， z 值描述滚轮的前滚或后滚。

english: An enum that describes what kind of input is being pressed. For types of input like Keyboard, this describes what key was pressed. For input like mousebutton, this provides no additional information.
translation: 一个描述此输入按键种类的枚举。针对键盘输入，描述按下的按键。针对鼠标按钮输入，不提供其他额外信息。

english: Smoothly moves a GuiObject from its current position to 'endPosition'. The only required argument is 'endPosition'. More info
translation: 将一个 GuiObject 从当前位置平滑地移动至 'endPosition'。唯一的必要参数为 'endPosition'。更多信息

english: Smoothly translates a GuiObject's current size to 'endSize'. The only required argument is 'endSize'. More info
translation: 将一个 GuiObject 从当前大小平滑地形变至 'endSize'。唯一的必要参数为 'endSize'。更多信息

english: Smoothly translates a GuiObject's current size to 'endSize', and also smoothly translates the GuiObject's current position to 'endPosition'. The only required arguments are 'endSize' and 'endPosition'. More info
translation: 将一个 GuiObject 从当前大小平滑地形变至 'endSize'，并将其从当前位置平滑地移动至 'endPosition'。唯一的必要参数为 'endSize' 和 'endPosition'。更多信息

english: If true, this GuiObject can fire mouse events and will pass them to any GuiObjects layered underneath, while false will do neither.
translation: 若值为 true，此 GuiObject 可触发鼠标事件并将其传递给下层 GuiObject，若值为 false 则无上述功能。

english: A Color3 value that specifies the background color for the GuiObject. This value is ignored if the Style property (not found on all GuiObjects) is set to something besides custom.
translation: 一个为 GuiObject 指定背景色的 Color3 值。若 Style 属性 (并非在所有 GuiObject 中都存在) 为非 Custom 的值，则此数值将被忽略。

english: A number value that specifies how transparent the background of the GuiObject is. This value is ignored if the Style property (not found on all GuiObjects) is set to something besides custom.
translation: 一个为 GuiObject 指定背景透明度的数值。若 Style 属性 (并非在所有 GuiObject 中都存在) 为非 Custom 的值，则此数值将被忽略。

english: A Color3 value that specifies the color of the outline of the GuiObject. This value is ignored if the Style property (not found on all GuiObjects) is set to something besides custom.
translation: 一个为 GuiObject 指定轮廓颜色的 Color3 值。若 Style 属性 (并非在所有 GuiObject 中都存在) 为非 Custom 的值，则此数值将被忽略。

english: A number value that specifies the thickness (in pixels) of the outline of the GuiObject. Currently this value can only be set to either 0 or 1, any other number has no effect. This value is ignored if the Style property (not found on all GuiObjects) is set to something besides custom.
translation: 一个为 GuiObject 指定轮廓粗细的数值 (以像素为单位)。目前此值只能被设为 0 或 1，任何其他数字均无效。若 Style 属性 (并非在所有 GuiObject 中都存在) 为非 Custom 的值，则此数值将被忽略。

english: If set to true, any descendants of this GuiObject will only render if contained within it's borders. If set to false, all descendants will render regardless of position.
translation: 若值设为 true，此 GuiObject 的所有后代只有在其边框内才会被渲染。若值设为 false，所有后代无论位置均会被渲染。

english: If true, allows a GuiObject to be dragged by the user's mouse. The events 'DragBegin' and 'DragStopped' are fired when the appropriate action happens, and only will fire on Draggable=true GuiObjects.
translation: 若值为 true，允许 GuiObject 被用户的鼠标拖动。'DragBegin' 和 'DragStopped' 事件将会在相应操作发生时触发，且只会在 Draggable=true 的 GuiObject 上触发。

english: A UDim2 value describing the size of the GuiObject on screen in both absolute and relative coordinates. More information on UDim2 is available here.
translation: 一个描述 GuiObject 在屏幕的绝对和相对坐标上的大小的 UDim2 值。更多关于 UDim2 的信息请参阅这里。

english: A UDim2 value describing the position of the top-left corner of the GuiObject on screen. More information on UDim2 is available here.
translation: 一个描述 GuiObject 的左上角在屏幕上的位置的 UDim2 值。更多关于 UDim2 的信息请参阅这里。"

english: The direction(s) that an object can be resized in. More info.
translation: 对象可以调整大小的方向。更多信息。

english: Describes the ordering in which overlapping GuiObjects will be drawn. A value of 1 is drawn first, while higher values are drawn in ascending order (each value draws over the last).
translation: 描述绘制 GuiObject 的叠加顺序。值为 1 时首先绘制，后续按值的升序依次绘制 (较大的值绘制在较小的值上方)。

english: Overrides the default selection adornment (used for gamepads). For best results, this should point to a GuiObject.
translation: 覆盖默认选择装饰 (用于游戏手柄)。为了获得最佳效果，应指向一个 GuiObject。

english: Fired when a GuiObject with Draggable set to true starts to be dragged. 'InitialPosition' is a UDim2 value of the position of the GuiObject before any drag operation began.
translation: Draggable 设为 true 的 GuiObject 被拖动时触发。'InitialPosition' 是一个记录 GuiObject 在拖动开始前位置的 UDim2 值。

english: Always fired after a DragBegin event, DragStopped is fired when the user releases the mouse button causing a drag operation on the GuiObject. Arguments 'x', and 'y' specify the top-left absolute position of the GuiObject when the event is fired.
translation: 总是在 DragBegin 事件后触发。DragStopped 在用户松开导致 GuiObject 拖动操作的鼠标按键后触发。参数 'x' 和 'y' 指定事件触发时 GuiObject 左上角的绝对位置。

english: Fired when the mouse enters a GuiObject, as long as the GuiObject is active (see active property for more detail). Arguments 'x', and 'y' specify the absolute pixel position of the mouse.
translation: 只要 GuiObject 处于活跃状态 (参阅活跃属性了解更多详细信息)，当鼠标进入 GuiObject 时触发。参数 'x' 和 'y' 指定鼠标的绝对像素位置。

english: Fired when the mouse leaves a GuiObject, as long as the GuiObject is active (see active property for more detail). Arguments 'x', and 'y' specify the absolute pixel position of the mouse.
translation: 只要 GuiObject 处于活跃状态 (参阅活跃属性了解更多详细信息)，但鼠标离开 GuiObject 时触发。参数 'x' 和 'y' 指定鼠标的绝对像素位置。

english: Fired when the mouse is inside a GuiObject and moves, as long as the GuiObject is active (see active property for more detail). Arguments 'x', and 'y' specify the absolute pixel position of the mouse.
translation: 只要 GuiObject 处于活跃状态 (参阅活跃属性了解更多详细信息)，当鼠标在 GuiObject 内移动时触发。参数 'x' 和 'y' 指定鼠标的绝对像素位置。

english: Fired when a user taps their finger on a TouchEnabled device. 'touchPositions' is a Lua array of Vector2, each indicating the position of all the fingers involved in the tap gesture. This event only fires locally.  This event will always fire regardless of game state.
translation: 当用户在 TouchEnabled 设备上轻触手指时触发。 'touchPositions' 是一个 Vector2 的 Lua 数组，其成员各自代表轻触手势中涉及的所有手指的位置。此事件仅在本地触发。无论游戏状态如何，此事件总是会触发。

english: Fired when a user pinches their fingers on a TouchEnabled device. 'touchPositions' is a Lua array of Vector2, each indicating the position of all the fingers involved in the pinch gesture. 'scale' is a float that indicates the difference from the beginning of the pinch gesture. 'velocity' is a float indicating how quickly the pinch gesture is happening. 'state' indicates the Enum.UserInputState of the gesture.  This event only fires locally.
translation: 当用户在启用 TouchEnabled 的设备上捏合手指时触发。'touchPositions' 是一个 Vector2 Lua 数组，其成员各自代表捏合手势中所涉及的全部手指的位置。 'scale' 是一个代表从捏合手势开始的差异值的浮点数。'velocity' 是一个代表捏合手势发生速度的浮点数。'state' 代表手势的 the Enum.UserInputState。此事件仅在本地触发。

english: Fired when a user swipes their fingers on a TouchEnabled device. 'swipeDirection' is an Enum.SwipeDirection, indicating the direction the user swiped. 'numberOfTouches' is an int that indicates how many touches were involved with the gesture.  This event only fires locally.
translation: 当用户在启用 TouchEnabled 的设备上滑动手指时触发。'swipeDirection' 是一个代表用户滑动方向的 Enum.SwipeDirection。 'numberOfTouches' 是一个代表该手势中涉及的触碰数量的整数。此事件仅在本地触发。

english: Fired when a user holds at least one finger for a short amount of time on the same screen position on a TouchEnabled device. 'touchPositions' is a Lua array of Vector2, each indicating the position of all the fingers involved in the gesture. 'state' indicates the Enum.UserInputState of the gesture.  This event only fires locally.
translation: 当用户在启用 TouchEnabled 的设备上用至少一根手指在同一屏幕位置短暂停留时触发。'touchPositions' 是一个 Vector2 Lua 数组，其成员各自代表该手势中涉及的所有手指的位置。'state' 代表手势的 Enum.UserInputState。此事件仅在本地触发。

english: Fired when a user rotates two fingers on a TouchEnabled device. 'touchPositions' is a Lua array of Vector2, each indicating the position of all the fingers involved in the gesture. 'rotation' is a float indicating how much the rotation has gone from the start of the gesture. 'velocity' is a float that indicates how quickly the gesture is being performed. 'state' indicates the Enum.UserInputState of the gesture.  This event only fires locally.
translation: 当用户在启用 TouchEnabled 的设备上旋转两根手指时触发。'touchPositions' 是一个 Vector2 Lua 数组，其成员各自代表该手势中涉及的所有手指的位置。'rotation' 是一个代表手势从初始位置旋转角度的浮点数。'velocity' 是一个代表旋转手势发生速度的浮点数。'state' 代表手势的 Enum.UserInputState。此事件仅在本地触发。

english: Fired when a user drags at least one finger on a TouchEnabled device. 'touchPositions' is a Lua array of Vector2, each indicating the position of all the fingers involved in the gesture. 'totalTranslation' is a Vector2, indicating how far the pan gesture has gone from its starting point. 'velocity' is a Vector2 that indicates how quickly the gesture is being performed in each dimension. 'state' indicates the Enum.UserInputState of the gesture.
translation: 当用户在启用 TouchEnabled 的设备上拖动至少一根手指时触发。'touchPositions' 是一个 Vector2 Lua 数组，其成员各自代表该手势中涉及的所有手指的位置。'totalTranslation' 是一个 Vector2，代表拖动手势从初始位置所行进的距离。'velocity' 是一个代表手势在各维度上行进速度的 Vector2。'state' 代表手势的 Enum.UserInputState。

english: Fired when a user begins interacting via a Human-Computer Interface device (Mouse button down, touch begin, keyboard button down, etc.). 'inputObject' is an InputObject, which contains useful data for querying user input.  This event only fires locally.
translation: 当用户开始通过人机交互设备进行交互 (按下鼠标按钮、触碰开始、按下键盘按键等) 时触发。'inputObject' 是一个包含查询用户输入的有用数据的 InputObject。此事件仅在本地触发。

english: Fired when a user changes interacting via a Human-Computer Interface device (Mouse move, touch move, mouse wheel, etc.). 'inputObject' is an InputObject, which contains useful data for querying user input.  This event only fires locally.
translation: 当用户通过人机交互设备变更交互 (鼠标移动、触碰移动、鼠标滚轮等) 时触发。'inputObject' 是一个包含查询用户输入的有用数据的 InputObject。此事件仅在本地触发。

english: Fired when a user stops interacting via a Human-Computer Interface device (Mouse button up, touch end, keyboard button up, etc.). 'inputObject' is an InputObject, which contains useful data for querying user input.  This event only fires locally.
translation: 当用户停止通过人机交互设备进行交互 (松开鼠标按钮、触碰结束、松开键盘按键等) 时触发。'inputObject' 是一个包含查询用户输入的有用数据的 InputObject。此事件仅在本地触发。

english: A container object used to layout other GUI objects
translation: 用于布局其他 GUI 对象的容器对象

english: Determines how a frame will look. Uses Enum.FrameStyle. More info
translation: 决定框架的外观。使用 Enum.FrameStyle。更多信息

english: Determines whether or not scrolling is allowed on this frame. If turned off, no scroll bars will be rendered.
translation: 决定此框架内是否允许滚动。若禁用，将不会渲染滚动条。

english: Determines the size of the area that is scrollable. The UDim2 is calculated using the parent gui's size, similar to the regular Size property on gui objects.
translation: 决定可滚动的区域大小。使用父 GUI 的大小计算 UDim2，类似 GUI 对象的常规 Size 属性。

english: The absolute position the scroll frame is in respect to the canvas size. The minimum this can be set to is (0,0), while the max is the absolute canvas size - AbsoluteWindowSize.
translation: 滚动框架相对画布大小的绝对位置。最小值可设为 (0,0)，最大值为画布的绝对尺寸 - AbsoluteWindowSize。

english: The size in pixels of the frame, without the scrollbars.
translation: 框架的尺寸，以像素为单位，滚动条不计入内。

english: How thick the scroll bar appears. This applies to both the horizontal and vertical scroll bars. Can be set to 0 for no bars render.
translation: 滚动条的厚度。同样适用于水平和垂直滚动条。设为 0 则不渲染滚动条。

english: The "Up" image on the vertical scrollbar. Size of this is always ScrollBarThickness by ScrollBarThickness. This is also used as the "left" image on the horizontal scroll bar.
translation: 垂直滚动条的“上”图像。大小始终为 ScrollBarThickness x ScrollBarThickness。还可以作为水平滚动条的“左”图像。

english: The "Middle" image on the vertical scrollbar. Size of this can vary in the y direction, but is always set at ScrollBarThickness in x direction. This is also used as the "mid" image on the horizontal scroll bar.
translation: 垂直滚动条的“中间”图像。此图像的大小可以在 y 轴产生变化，但在 x 轴方向上其值应始终为 ScrollBarThickness。还可以作为水平滚动条的“中间”图像。

english: The "Down" image on the vertical scrollbar. Size of this is always ScrollBarThickness by ScrollBarThickness. This is also used as the "right" image on the horizontal scroll bar.
translation: 垂直滚动条的“下”图像。大小始终为 ScrollBarThickness x ScrollBarThickness。还可以作为水平滚动条的“右”图像。

english: A GUI object containing an Image
translation: 包含图片的 GUI 对象

english: Specifies the id of the texture to display. More info
translation: 指定要显示的纹理的 ID。更多信息

english: Specifies how an image should be displayed. See ScaleType for more info.
translation: 指定图片的显示方式。更多信息请参阅 ScaleType。

english: If ScaleType is set to Slice, this Rect is used to specify the central part of the image. Everything outside of this is considered to be the border.
translation: 若 ScaleType 设为 Slice，此 Rect 用于指定图片的中心部分。除此以外的一切均被视为边缘。

english: If ScaleType is set to Tile, this sets the size of the tile.
translation: 若 ScaleType 设为 Tile，此项将设置地砖的大小。
含有文本的 GUI 对象
包含文本的 GUI 按钮

english: A GUI button containing an Image
translation: 包含图片的 GUI 按钮

english: Determines whether a button changes color automatically when reacting to mouse events.
translation: 决定一个按钮在响应鼠标事件时是否自动改变颜色。

english: Allows the mouse to be free in first person mode. If a button with this property set to true is visible, the mouse is 'free' in first person mode.
translation: 允许鼠标在第一人称模式下自由移动。若一个此属性被设为 true，则按钮可见，鼠标也可以在第一人称模式下“自由”移动。

english: Determines how a button will look, including mouse event states. Uses Enum.ButtonStyle. More info
translation: 决定一个按钮的外观，包括鼠标事件状态。使用 Enum.ButtonStyle。更多信息

english: Fired when the mouse is over the button, and the mouse down and up events fire without the mouse leaving the button.
translation: 当鼠标悬停在按钮上且未离开按钮，鼠标键按下和松开事件触发时触发。

english: Fired when the mouse button is pushed down on a button.
translation: 当鼠标键按下按钮时触发。

english: Fired when the mouse button is released on a button.
translation: 当鼠标键从按钮上松开时触发。

english: This function currently does not work :(
This function currently does not work :(
This function currently does not work :(
A GUI that can show 3D objects
translation: 可以显示 3D 对象的 GUI

english: A number value that specifies how transparent the rendered image of the ViewportFrame is
translation: 一个指定 ViewportFrame 的渲染图像的透明度的数值

english: The rendered image of the ViewportFrame will be multiplied by this color
translation: ViewportFrame 中渲染的图像将会增加此颜色的比重

english: Changing this changes the color tint of all objects in the ViewportFrame.
translation: 修改此项会更改 ViewportFrame 中所有对象的颜色色调。

english: Directional light color for objects in the ViewportFrame.
translation: ViewportFrame 中对象的定向光照颜色

english: Light direction. Value will be normalized. All values valid except (0,0,0).
translation: 光照方向。取值将被标准化。除 (0,0,0) 外，所有值均有效。

english: A GUI button containing an Image
translation: 包含图片的 GUI 按钮

english: Specifies the asset id of the texture to display. More info
translation: 指定要显示的纹理的素材 ID。更多信息

english: Specifies how an image should be displayed. See ScaleType for more info.
translation: 指定图片的显示方式。更多信息请参阅 ScaleType。

english: If ScaleType is set to Slice, this Rect is used to specify the central part of the image. Everything outside of this is considered to be the border.
translation: 若 ScaleType 设为 Slice，此 Rect 用于指定图片的中心部分。除此以外的一切均被视为边缘。

english: If ScaleType is set to Tile, this sets the size of the tile.
translation: 若 ScaleType 设为 Tile，此项设置地砖的大小。

english: A 3D GUI object to represent draggable handles
translation: 用于代表可拖动手柄的 3D GUI 对象

english: A 3D GUI object to represent draggable arc handles
translation: 用于代表可拖动弧形手柄的 3D GUI 对象

english: A 3D GUI object to represent the visible selection around an object
translation: 用于代表一个对象周围可见选择范围的 3D GUI 对象

english: A 3D GUI object to represent the visible selection around an object
translation: 用于代表一个对象周围可见选择范围的 3D GUI 对象

english: A 3D GUI object to represent the visible selection around a face of an object
translation: 用于代表一个对象的一个面周围可见选择范围的 3D GUI 对象

english: An object that can be placed under parts to hold Value objects that represent that part's configuration
translation: 一个可以置于部件之下，用于存放代表该部件配置的 Value 对象的对象

english: An object that specifies the appearance of Humanoid characters
translation: 一个指定 Humanoid 角色外观的对象

english: An object that can be created to hold and organize objects
translation: 一个可创建用于存放和整理对象的对象

english: A visual line drawn representation between two part objects
translation: 两个部件对象之间绘制可视线表示

english: A visual line drawn representation between two positions
translation: 两个位置之间绘制可视线表示

english: A visual line drawn representation between two parts.
translation: 两个部件之间绘制可视线表示

english: The pose of a joint relative to it's parent part in a keyframe
translation: 关节在关键帧中相对其父部件的姿态

english: Represents when an event should be fired in an animation
translation: 代表一个事件应该在动画中触发

english: Represents a linked animation object, containing keyframes and poses.
translation: 代表一个关联动画对象，包含关键帧和姿态。

english: Returned by a call to LoadAnimation. Controls the playback of an animation on a Humanoid.
translation: 通过调用 LoadAnimation 返回。控制 Humanoid 上动画的播放。

english: Allows animations to be played on joints of the parent object.
translation: 允许在父对象的关节上播放动画。

english: Modifies the appearance of a body part.
An object used to make dialog trees to converse with players
translation: 用于创建对话框树与玩家交谈的对象

english: The maximum distance that the player's character can be from the dialog's parent in order to use the dialog.
translation: 玩家角色使用对话框时与对话框父类的最远距离。

english: Indicates whether or not an extra choice is available for the player to exit the dialog tree at this node.
translation: 表明是否有额外的选项让玩家在此节点退出对话框树。

english: The prompt text for an extra choice that allows the player to exit the dialog tree at this node.
translation: 让玩家在此节点退出对话框树的额外选项的提示文本。

english: Indicates whether or not the dialog is currently being used by one or more players.
translation: 表明对话框当前是否正被一个或以上玩家使用。

english: The chat message that is displayed to the player when they first activate the dialog.
translation: 玩家首次激活对话框时向其显示的聊天信息。

english: Describes the purpose of the dialog, which is used to display a relevant icon on the dialog's activation button.
translation: 描述对话框的用途，用于在对话框的激活按钮上显示相关图标。

english: Describes the tone of the dialog, which is used to display a relevant color in the dialog interface.
translation: 描述对话框的语气，用于在对话框界面显示相关颜色。

english: Indicates how the dialog may be used by players. Use Enum.DialogBehaviorType.SinglePlayer if only one player should interact with the dialog at a time, otherwise use Enum.DialogBehaviorType.MultiplePlayers.
translation: 表明玩家使用对话框的方式。若同一时间内只有一名玩家能与对话框互动，请使用 Enum.DialogBehaviorType.SinglePlayer，否则使用 Enum.DialogBehaviorType.MultiplePlayers。

english: Returns an array of the players currently conversing with this dialog.
translation: 返回一个包含正在与此对话框交谈的玩家的数组。

english: An object used to make dialog trees to converse with players
translation: 用于创建对话框树与玩家交谈的对象

english: A UnionOperation is a union of multiple parts
translation: UnionOperation 是多个部件的组合

english: Override the colors of the mesh with the part color.
translation: 使用部件颜色覆盖网格颜色。

english: A NegateOperation can be used to create holes in other parts
translation: NegateOperation 可用于在其他部件上挖孔

english: Override the colors of the mesh with the part color.
translation: 使用部件颜色覆盖网格颜色。

english: A MeshPart is a physically simulatable mesh
translation: MeshPart 是一种可模拟物理特性的网格

english: Object representing a high performance bounded grid of static 4x4 parts
translation: 代表一种静态 4x4 部件的高性能有界栅格的对象

english: Makes the parent part emit light in a spherical shape
translation: 使父部件发出球形光线

english: Makes the parent part emit light in a conical shape
translation: 使父部件发出圆锥形光线

english: Makes the parent part emit light in a frustum shape from rectangle defined by part
translation: 使父部件发出基于部件形状的矩形光线

english: Allow functions defined in one script to be called by another script across client/server boundary
translation: 允许一个脚本中定义的函数跨越客户端/服务器界限被另一个脚本调用

english: Allow events defined in one script to be subscribed to by another script across client/server boundary
translation: 允许一个脚本中定义的事件跨越客户端/服务器界限被另一个脚本订阅

english: Object representing a snapshot of the region of terrain
translation: 一个代表地形区域快照的对象

english: A script fragment. Only runs when another script uses require() on it.
translation: 一个脚本片段。仅在其他脚本对其使用 require() 时运行。

english: If 'functionToBind' from ContextActionService:BindAction() returns Enum.ContextActionResult.Sink, the input event will stop at that function and no other bound actions under it will be invoked. This is the default behavior if 'functionToBind' does not return anything or yields in any way.
translation: 若 ContextActionService:BindAction() 的 'functionToBind' 返回 Enum.ContextActionResult.Sink，则输入事件在该函数处停止，且不会调用其下的其他绑定操作。此行为是 'functionToBind' 未返回内容或因任意方式而暂停时的默认行为。

english: If 'functionToBind' from ContextActionService:BindAction() returns Enum.ContextActionResult.Pass, the input event is considered to have not been handled by 'functionToBind' and will continue being passed to actions bound to the same input type.
translation: 若 ContextActionService:BindAction() 的 'functionToBind' 返回 Enum.ContextActionResult.Pass，则输入事件被视为未经 'functionToBind' 处理，并将继续传递给绑定至相同输入类型的操作。

english: The ordering to use for sorting an array of GuiObjects.
translation: 排序一个 GuiObject 数组时使用的顺序。

english: Sort by alphabetical ordering of the Name property.
translation: 根据 Name 属性的字母顺序进行排序。

english: Sort using the less than operator on the LayoutOrder property of GuiObject.
translation: 使用 GuiObject 的 LayoutOrder 属性的小于运算符进行排序。

english: Controls the behavior of the ZIndex property.
translation: 控制 ZIndex 属性的行为。

english: The ZIndex property will override the default value computed from the depth in the hierarchy.
translation: ZIndex 属性会覆盖由层次结构底层计算得出的默认值。

english: The ZIndex property will control the order that the GuiObject will be rendered relative to its siblings.
translation: ZIndex 属性会控制 GuiObject 相对其同级的渲染顺序。

english: Controls how an image is displayed.
Force the image to fill the available space.
translation: 强制使用图像填充可用空间。

english: Use the SliceCenter property to stretch the middle of the image but maintain crisp borders.
translation: 使用 SliceCenter 属性拉伸图像中央但维持清晰边缘。

english: Tile the image using the TileSize property.
translation: 使用 TileSize 属性平铺图像。

english: Size the image to the largest size that will fit in the available space while maintaining aspect ratio.
translation: 将图像调整为适合可用空间的最大尺寸，同时保持宽高比。

english: Fill the available space, maintaining aspect ratio by cropping the edges if necessary.
translation: 填充可用空间，必要时通过裁剪边缘来维持宽高比。

english: A container instance that contains Scripts.  Useful only for Plugins.  When Studio starts, we load plugins into the 'UserPlugin' data model and execute Scripts contained in StandalonePluginScripts container. If a plugin doesn't have such a container then the plugin isn't loaded into UserPlugin data model.  When a data model for a place is created (e.g. the Edit data model), we load plugins into said data model and execute only those Scripts which are not contained in StandalonePluginScripts container.
translation: 一个包含 Script 的容器实例。仅适合配合插件使用。当 Studio 启动后，我们会将插件载入 'UserPlugin' 数据模型并执行包含在 StandalonePluginScripts 容器中的 Script。若某个插件不包含此容器，则插件不会被载入 UserPlugin 数据模型。在创建一个场景的数据模型（如 Edit 数据模型）后，我们会将插件载入上述数据模型并只执行未包含在 StandalonePluginScripts 容器中的 Script。

english: The SphereHandleAdornment is a sphere that can be adorned to a BasePart.
translation: SphereHandleAdornment 是可被装饰于 BasePart 的球体。

english: An object that contains a World. Supports rigid joints. Unlike Workspace, WorldModels do not support dynamics simulation.
translation: 包含一个世界的对象。支持刚性关节。与工作区不同，WorldModels 不支持动态模拟。

english: The LineHandleAdornment is a line that can be adorned to a BasePart.
translation: LineHandleAdornment 是可被装饰于 BasePart 的线。

english: The (sequence of) color3 of the gradient.
translation: 颜色渐变的 color3 （的序列）。

english: Sets scale [0-1] of Specular Environment Lighting to add to Ambient.
translation: 设置添加至环境的镜面环境光源的比例 [0-1]。

english: A ConeHandleAdornment is a cone that can be adorned to a BasePart.
translation: ConeHandleAdornment 是可被装饰于 BasePart 的圆锥体。

english: The ImageHandleAdornment is an image that can be adorned to a BasePart.
translation: ImageHandleAdornment 是可被装饰于 BasePart 的图片。

english: The Motor6D object is used to make movable joints between two Parts.
translation: Motor6D 对象用于在两个部件之间制作可动的关节。

english: The BoxHandleAdornment is a rectangular prism that can be adorned to a BasePart.
translation: BoxHandleAdornment 是可被装饰于 BasePart 的长方体。

english: Apply a gradient to the parent GuiObject.
translation: 向父 GuiObject 添加渐变效果。

english: The CylinderHandleAdornment is a cylinder that can be adorned to a BasePart.
translation: CylinderHandleAdornment 是可被装饰于 BasePart 的圆柱体。

english: Sets scale [0-1] of Diffuse Environment Lighting to add to Ambient.
translation: 设置添加至环境的扩散环境光源的比例 [0-1]。

english: Offset of gradient center in scale.
The (sequence of) transparency of the gradient.
translation: 颜色渐变的透明度（的序列）。

english: Overrides the visual appearance of a parent MeshPart
translation: 覆盖父项 MeshPart 的视觉外观

english: Determines how the ColorMap's alpha channel behaves.
translation: 决定了 ColorMap 的 Alpha 通道行为。

english: Image ID used to color the surface. If left empty, surface uses Part Color. Not scriptable at runtime.
translation: 用来为表面着色的图像 ID。若为空则表面将使用 Part Color。无法在运行时中进行脚本编辑。

english: Grayscale Image ID that determines the metalness of the surface. Not scriptable at runtime.
translation: 决定了表面金属外观的灰度图像 ID。在运行时中无法进行脚本编辑。

english: Image ID of the normal map used to control surface bumps and curvature. Not scriptable at runtime.
translation: 用以控制表面隆起及弯曲的普通地图图像 ID。在运行时中无法进行脚本编辑。

english: Grayscale Image ID that determines the roughness of the surface. Not scriptable at runtime.
translation: 决定了表面粗糙程度的灰度图像 ID。在运行时中无法进行脚本编辑。

english: Modify corner properties of parent GuiObject.
translation: 修改父项 GuiObject 的边角属性。
拥有特定半径的圆形边角。

english: A value that controls the air particulates density. The proportion of airborne particles per unit of view depth between the camera and the sky.
translation: 控制空气中粒子密度的值，也就是镜头与天空之间每个视深单元中浮空粒子的比例。

english: A value that offsets the quantity of light scattering events among particles in the atmosphere between the camera and the sky.
translation: 用以偏移镜头与天空间大气中粒子间光散射事件数量的值。

english: A value that controls the height of fog in the atmosphere above the horizon (not volumetric...yet...).
translation: 控制地平线以上大气中雾气高度的值（尚未体积化）。

english: A Color3 value that changes the hue of the atmosphere, mixed with the sky color.
translation: 混合天空颜色改变气氛色调的 Color3 值。

english: A Color3 value for the the hue the atmosphere takes on away from the sun towards the horizon, mixed with the sky color (aka extinction).
translation: 当大气远离太阳接近地平线时混合天空颜色所呈现的色调 Color3 值（也就是大气消光现象）。

english: A value that controls the haziness of the atmosphere between the camera and the sky (aka turbidity).
translation: 控制了镜头与天空之间大气朦胧度的值（也就是大气浊度）。

english: A value that increases the glow of the atmosphere around light the sun.
translation: 增加阳光附近大气光晕的值。

english: Depth based blur (Depth of Field) effect.
Controls the distance in stud units away from the camera where are in focus.
translation: 控制焦点处与镜头之间的格数单位距离。

english: Controls the distance in stud units away from the FocusDistance where both in front and behind objects can begin to blur.
translation: 控制对象的前后都能够开始模糊处理时与 FocusDistance 之间的格数单位距离。

english: Maximum intensity of the near blur -the higher the Intensity, the stronger the blur is allowed to reach.
translation: 近景模糊最大强度：Intensity（强度）越大，模糊可达到距离越大。

english: Maximum intensity of the far blur -the higher the Intensity, the stronger the blur is allowed to reach.
translation: 远景模糊最大强度：Intensity（强度）越大，模糊可达到距离越大。

english: A container whose contents should be scripts. Scripts that are added to the container are run on the server and the client.
translation: 一个内容应为脚本的容器。添加到容器的脚本将在服务器和客户端上运行。
管理从 roblox.com 安装的插件
发生错误。请尝试再次更新。

english: An unexpected thing happened, try again
Click and hold to add terrain.
translation: 单击并按住以增加地形。

english: Click and hold to erode and remove terrain.
translation: 单击并按住以侵蚀和移除地形。

english: Click and hold to grow and expand terrain.
translation: 单击并按住以增长和扩大地形。

english: Paint the material of the terrain.

translation: 对平滑的地形区域进行操作。

english: Brush to smooth out rough or jagged terrain.
translation: 用笔刷平滑参差不平的地形。

english: Click and hold to remove terrain.
translation: 单击并按住以移除地形。

english: Valid HeightMap required to begin importing Terrain.
translation: 需要有效的 HeightMap 才能开始导入地形。

english: Game must be published before importing terrain.
translation: 必须在导入地形前发布游戏。

english: Size of region must be defined.
Game must be published before importing terrain.
translation: 必须在导入地形前发布游戏。

english: Do you want to clear all terrain?
Valid HeightMap required to begin importing Terrain.
translation: 需要有效的 HeightMap 才能开始导入地形。

english: Generating with size ({1}) at position ({2}) using seed {3} and biomes: {4}
translation: 使用种子 {3} 和生态：{4} 在位置 ({2}) 上以尺寸 ({1}) 进行生成

english: Terrain instance could not be found.

translation: 转换完成：{2:int} 个实例，用时 {1} 秒

english: Select Parts or Models containing Parts to convert to terrain
translation: 选择部件或包含部件的模型来转换为地形

english: Only Parts or Models containing Parts can be converted
translation: 只有部件或包含部件的模型可被转换

english: Parts with size dimensions below 4 studs may produce incorrect results
translation: 大小在 4 格以下的部件可能会产生错误的结果

english: Only Parts can be converted, other objects will be skipped
translation: 只有部件可被转换，其他对象将被跳过
正在将部件转换至生态

english: Terrain importer only works in edit mode.
translation: 地形导入器只能在编辑模式中运行。

english: Image is not a valid file.
Only 8 bit and 16 bit PNGs are supported.
translation: 只支持 8 位和 16 位 PNG 图像。

english: Image has invalid number of channels.
An import operation is already in progress.
When you import a color image, the importer only reads the red channel to create a greyscale heightmap. The other channels have been discarded.
translation: 当导入彩色图像时，导入程序只会读取红色通道以创建灰度 heightmap。其他通道将被忽略。

english: Image aspect ratio ({1}) is not compatible with Size values (X {2:int}, Z {3:int}). For best results, adjust the Size or import a new image.
translation: 图像的高宽比（{1}）与 Size（尺寸）值（X {2:int}，Z {3:int}）不兼容。要获得最佳效果，请调整 Size 或导入新图像.

english: Image resolution ({1:int}x{2:int}) is too low for the target Size values (X {3:int}, Z {4:int}). For best results, decrease the size or import a new Heightmap.
translation: 图像的分辨率（{1:int}x{2:int}）与目标 Size（尺寸）值（X {3:int}，Z {4:int}）相比过小。要获得最佳效果，请缩小 Size 或导入新 Heightmap。

english: Colormaps convert image colors to terrain materials using Roblox Studio's color key.
translation: Colormaps 用 Roblox Studio 的色彩键将图像颜色转换为地形材质。

english: Colormap RGB values are out of range.
The imported colormap contains RGB values that do not match the Colormap Index. The generated materials might not be correct. Please ensure you’re using the sRGB colorspace for best results.
translation: 导入的 colormap 包含不符合 Colormap 索引的 RGB 值。生成的材质可能不正确。请确保你使用的是 sRGB 色域以获得最佳效果。

english: The imported colormap contains RGB values that do not match the Colormap Index.
translation: 导入的 colormap 包含不符合 Colormap 索引的 RGB 值。

english: Edit/apply plane when using plane lock in manual mode
translation: 在手动模式中启用平面锁定时编辑 / 应用平面

english: Click Upgrade to improve the way water joins with terrain at the shores.
translation: 点按升级，提高水与海岸地形连接的方式。

english: The upgrade will only be applied to this place. This will automatically adjust shallow water shape on existing shorelines. You might want to review and hand-edit the results afterwards, especially around streams, waterfalls and any other non-horizontal water surfaces. The upgrade can be reverted right after its completion using the Undo command.
translation: 升级仅适用于此场景。这将自动调整现有海岸线的浅水形状。你可能之后会想要审核并手动编辑呈现效果，尤其是在水流、瀑布和其他非横向的水面。升级可以通过“撤销“命令完成后立即还原。
点按 [link] 了解更多信息。

english: Would you like to upgrade this place's terrain with the new shorelines?
translation: 你想要使用全新的海岸线功能升级此场景的地形吗？

english: You can also upgrade this place's shorelines later from the Terrain Editor panel. The upgrade can be reverted right after its completion with the Undo command.

视频处理中 - 请稍候...

english: Our moderation team is taking a look – we'll be in touch shortly.
translation: 我们的审核团队正在核对，我们将尽快与您取得联系。

english: We encountered an error. Please try again in a bit, and if you continue to see this error, you may need to try a new video.
translation: 发生错误，请稍后重试。如果你持续遇到此问题，请尝试使用新视频。

english: Your animation did not comply with our moderation rules. Please try a different video.
translation: 你的动画没有遵守我们的审核标准，请尝试使用其他视频。

english: That video is too long – try a video shorter than 15 seconds.
translation: 视频过长，请使用 15 秒以内的视频。

english: Couldn't detect a person – try a video with a person fully in frame, facing the camera.
translation: 无法检测到人物，请使用含有全身入镜，面对镜头的人物视频。

english: That video is too shaky – try a more stable video.
translation: 视频摇晃幅度过大，请使用拍摄更稳定的视频。

english: Sorry, we're unable to process your video right now due to a high volume of requests. Please try again in a bit.
translation: 抱歉，由于请求数量过大，目前我们无法处理你的视频。请稍后重试。

english: Your animation creation has been canceled.
Choose a short video (15 seconds or less) containing a single person, fully in frame. Try to use a video with a stable, unmoving camera.
translation: 选择含有全身入镜、单一人物的短视频（15 秒内）。请尽量使用镜头不摇晃的视频。

english: The Curve Editor is a new way to visually create and edit rich animations within the Animation Editor.
translation: 全新的曲线编辑器可以让你在动画编辑器中创作并编辑生动的视觉动画。

english: Multiple people detected - Please try a video with a single person fully in frame.
translation: 检测到多个人物，请选择含有全身入镜、单一人物的视频。

english: We're rolling this out slowly and unfortunately it's not available for you at this time. Please check back periodically to see if we have opened it up.
translation: 我们还在陆续推出此动能，很遗憾，当前你无法使用此功能。欢迎定期回来查看此功能是否开放权限。

english: Animate faces by recording your face movements directly from your webcam.
translation: 直接使用网络摄像头录制面部动作即可使用面部动画。

english: A camera is required to use this feature. Please make sure your camera is connected and powered on.
translation: 此功能需要使用摄像头。请确认摄像头已连接并开启电源。

english: Camera permission is required for this feature. You can enable it for RobloxStudio in your system settings.
translation: 此功能需要使用摄像头，你可以在系统设置中为 Roblox Studio 启用摄像头权限。

english: Multiple cameras have been detected. Please choose one to start recording.
translation: 检测到多个摄像头。请选择要使用的摄像头并开始录制。

english: We're rolling this out slowly and unfortunately it's not available for you at this time. Please check back periodically to see if we have opened it up.
translation: 我们还在陆续推出此动能，很遗憾，当前你无法使用此功能。欢迎定期回来查看此功能是否开放权限。

english: Allow video and facial movement collection?
translation: 允许收集视频和面部动作？

english: By clicking "Yes", you allow Roblox Studio to access your video camera and you consent to the collection and use of your facial movements as described in the Roblox Facial Animation Privacy Notice. Depending on your location, applicable laws might define this data as a biometric identifier or biometric information.
translation: 点按“是”，即表示你同意 Roblox Studio 访问你的摄像头，并同意 Roblox 将按照 Roblox 面部动画隐私声明收集并使用你的面部动作。根据你的所在地区，此数据可能会被视作生物识别鉴定特征或生物识别信息。

english: Existing face animation will be overwritten. The action is undoable (Cmd+Z / Ctrl+Z).
translation: 当前的面部动画将被覆盖。此动作将无法撤销（Command + Z / Ctrl + Z）。

translation: 如要在腾讯发布与运营的罗布乐思 App 发布作品，你需要注册腾讯账号并接受腾讯使用条款与隐私政策。[link]

translation: 新的游戏会话会在运行新版本的服务器上启动，运行旧版本的服务器将会持续到所有会话结束。

english: All existing servers are forced to shutdown in a few minutes upon publishing so that all players will join the latest version. It equals to publish and 'Shutdown all servers'.
translation: 所有当前服务器将在发布后的几分钟内强制关闭，所有玩家将加入运行新版本的服务器。此操作等同于“发布并关闭所有服务器”。

translation: 如果覆盖被拒绝，启用回滚到先前版本 [link]

english: By allowing HTTP requests, 3rd party developers are able to gather information on your machine. These might be harmless (such as crash logs) or malicious (such as gathering information on your game's scripts). Disabling HTTP requests might result in a non-working plugin.
translation: 允许 HTTP 请求运行后，第三方开发者将可以从您的电脑上收集各类信息。其中可能包括无害信息（例如崩溃日志等）或有害信息（例如您的游戏脚本信息等）。禁用 HTTP 请求可能会导致插件失效。

english: By allowing Script Injection, this plugin may insert or modify scripts that perform malicious actions anywhere in your game (scripts can pretty much do anything). Disabling Script Injection might result in a non-working plugin.
translation: 若允许脚本注入，此插件可能会通过注入或修改脚本在游戏中的任何地方进行恶意操作（脚本几乎是万能的）。禁用脚本注入则可能会使插件无法生效。

translation: 此体验仅限于经过年龄验证的 17 岁及以上创作者访问。

translation: 所有脚本问题都已解决。

translation: {count} 个脚本已恢复到还原前的状态。

translation: 点按“开始扫描”以开始扫描需要转换的动画、脚本和模型的场景。这可能需要一些时间。

translation: 此角色已成功转换为 R15。

translation: 无法获得素材的产品信息
上传失败：HTTP 错误代码 %d

english: Not all animations were replaced. Please use the Script Converter to complete replacement.
translation: 并未替换所有动画。请使用脚本转换器完成替换。

english: Select and convert R15 characters to replace the R6 characters in your experience.
translation: 在你的作品中选择并转换R15角色以替换R6角色。

english: The replacement rules will apply to the selected scripts when you convert them.
translation: 当你转换时，替换规则将应用于被选中的脚本。

english: Learn more about how conversion handles replacing characters and animation.
translation: 了解更多有关转换如何处理替代的角色及动画。

english: Something was found in your script that may cause problems, however it may not be required to fix.
translation: 你脚本中的部分内容或将引发问题，但非必须要修复。

english: Name must be updated in order to convert this script to be compatable with R15 gameplay.
translation: 名称必须更新以便转换脚本后与R15游戏兼容。

english: Select and accept the converted animations to replace the R6 animations in your experience.
translation: 在作品中选择并接受转换动画以代替R6动画。

english: No R6 characters found to convert in this experience.
translation: 本作品中未发现有待转换的R6角色。

english: No scripts with R6 references were found in this experience.
translation: 本作品中未发现带有R6引用的脚本。

english: No R6 animations were found to convert in this experience.
translation: 本作品中未发现待转换的R6动画。

english: Clean up temporary instances used for avatar compatability and backup data used during the conversion process.
translation: 清理用于虚拟形象兼容的临时实例和在转换过程中使用的备份数据。

english: Confirming finalization step is not reversible. Script backup data and any compatability layer instances on converted avatars will be deleted. Below are characters and scripts that have not been converted. Please check this list to make sure everything you need is converted before confirming.
translation: 完结步骤确认后将无法再恢复。脚本备份数据和转换虚拟形象的兼容层实例将被删除。以下是未转换的虚拟形象和脚本。请检查该列表，确保所有需要的内容均已转换再进行确认。

english: Finalization step is complete. Please test your experience.
translation: 完结步骤完成。请测试你的作品。

description: Title for the error dialog when Studio fails to launch
Error message is shown when the user doesn't have WebView2 installed. WebView2 is required for Studio to load the login page correctly.

translation: 需要安装 WebView2 才可启动 Studio。请点按此处了解安装详情。

description: Error when web credentials don't match Studio's existing credentials
english: Studio failed to open because your web account credentials do not match the current Studio account credentials.
translation: 无法打开 Studio，因为你的网站帐户凭证与当前 Studio 的帐户凭证不符。

description: This is shown as a header for an error dialog when Studio fails to launch
Error message is shown when Studio fails to load WebView dialog for multiple times due to unexpected error
english: An error occurred while launching Studio login. Please login on the website or try again later.
translation: 启动 Studio 登录时发生错误。请在网站登录并稍后重试。

description: This is shown as a header for an error dialog when Studio fails to launch
Error message is shown when Studio fails to load WebView dialog for multiple times due to unexpected error
english: An error occurred while logging into Studio. Please login on the website or try again later.
translation: 登录 Studio 时发生错误。请在网站登录并稍后重试。

description: Error message that is shown when Studio fails to open due to credential mismatch, specifically when the cookie credential mismatch token credential

translation: 登录 Studio 时发生错误。请关闭所有 Roblox 实例并重试。

description: Error message that is shown when Studio fails to open due to credential mismatch, e.g. user login two instance with account A and B at the same time and only one of them will success, the other one will receive this error message
english: Attempted login was unsuccessful because Studio is already logged in to another account. This Studio window will automatically close.
translation: 由于已有另一帐户登录 Studio，尝试登录失败。此 Studio 窗口将自动关闭。

description: Error message that is shown when Studio fails to open due to credential mismatch, e.g. user launch Studio from the web but ended up using a different credential to login studio than the original one from the web
english: Studio failed to open due to mismatched credentials. Please login with the current web account when launching from the web.
translation: 由于凭证不匹配，Studio 无法打开。从网站打开 Studio 时请使用当前登录到网站的帐户。

description: This is shown as a header for a dialog when Studio fails to login automatically from web due to lack of matching local credential
translation: 登录即可在 Studio 中继续

description: The text of the button for retrying the external login

english: An error occurred while logging into Studio. Please do not close Studio during login.
translation: 登录 Studio 时发生错误。请勿在登录过程中关闭 Studio。

description: Error message is shown when the user doesn't have WebView2 installed. WebView2 is required for Studio to load the login page correctly. However, user can still use browser to login
english: WebView2 installation required to load login page. Click here for installation details. Please login on the website.
translation: 需要安装 WebView2 才可启动 Studio。请点按此处了解安装详情。请在网站登录。

Discover Audio used in this place.

Any audio marked with a red cross should be replaced.

Select an asset to see a list of locations where it is used, and update each one to use a new asset id.

发现此场景使用的音频。

标有红叉的音频应被替换。

english:
The Audio Discovery plugin finds any audio assets used in this place and checks that they are licenced sound effects or owned by the creator of this place.

This place is not yet published so it has no associated creator. Publish it to ensure any sounds uploaded by the creator are marked as available.
translation:
音频发现插件将找到此场景使用的音频素材，并确认音频是否为授权音频，或由此场景的创作者拥有。

此场景尚未发布，因此没有对应的创作者。发布后即可确保创作者上传的音频将视为可用。

translation: 在浏览器中选择服装、配饰或头部以添加至预览。

translation: 检测到 1 则将阻止你上传至商城的警告

translation: 检测到 {amount:int} 则将阻止你上传至商城的警告

translation: 该虚拟形象可上传至商城

translation: 你想将这些物品添加至哪个面板？
